            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Nero Caesar</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Germanici Caesaris <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">divi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pron</abbr><ex>epos</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">flamen Augustalis</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">quaestor</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">Agrippina</supplied> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Agrippae <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan></supplied> divi <supplied reason="lost">Augusti nep</supplied>tis <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">uxor Germani</supplied>ci <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Caesaris mater</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Caesaris <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">Germanici principis</supplied> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">Drusus Caesar</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Ger<supplied reason="lost">manici Caesaris <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">divi Augusti <expan><abbr>pron</abbr><ex>epos</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">sodalis Augustalis</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">pontifex</supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: April 37 n. Chr. oder später. Ursprünglich drei Kolumnen; Buchstaben der zweiten und dritten Kolumnen erhalten. Anathyrosespuren an den Seiten weisen auf eine urpsprüngliche Einbindung des Blockes in ein größeres Monument.</p>
            </div>
